Shareholders in  Iberdrola Renovables
SA (IBR)  voted to support  Iberdrola SA (IBE) â€™s plan to buy out minority
investors in the clean-energy unit, and approved a special
dividend of 1.20 euros ($1.71) a share as part of the deal.  The plan won the support of 74 percent of minority
shareholders at a meeting in Valencia today, according to a
preliminary tally of the votes announced by Secretary to the
